{"tid":1280540,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"美斯炮轟：巴西控制了一切 球證漏判我們2個12碼","createTime":"2019-07-03T04:16:01.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-03T10:10:05.000Z","uid":173952,"like":55,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":44,"replies":[{"pid":"43cfa33b8053586096c77a048425b00259ee7d85","tid":1280540,"uid":173952,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-03T04:16:01.000Z","msg":"美洲盃4強阿根廷0-2不敵巴西，無緣決賽。賽後美斯炮轟球證，認為球證偏袒巴西，無視阿根廷的12碼。<br />\n<br />\n  美斯表達了對球證的不滿，他說：「他們在美洲盃一直都吹犯規，但沒有去看VAR，這是難以置信的。我希望南美足協能做點什麼，雖然我也知道他們什麼也不能做，巴西控制了一切，這情況很複雜。」<br />\n<br />\n  美斯指出，「我認為我們應該得到兩粒12碼，但是球證沒有吹罰。」<br />\n<br />\n  關於阿根廷的表現，美斯說：「除了結果，我們展現了我們能夠勝任這份任務，我認為我們踢了一場出色的比賽，我們盡了很大的努力，他們不比我們優秀很多。」"},{"pid":"294e96e25beb212a9e675718759719f458ba6955","tid":1280540,"uid":227312,"like":82,"dislike":13,"score":69,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-03T04:17:03.000Z","msg":"比你都唔入架啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2ef2ee069b856f676633983f91c9aad5a9ab23e1","tid":1280540,"uid":135957,"like":18,"dislike":0,"score":18,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-03T04:18:48.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"3cd7f3f129342d91a98a8247b9c06c25ed8006c3","tid":1280540,"uid":5290,"like":38,"dislike":3,"score":35,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-03T04:20:07.000Z","msg":"唔洗灰心<br />\n下年又有<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7db3e42e5cbc3767a9b958d3ddc889397f0a4677","tid":1280540,"uid":132264,"like":20,"dislike":0,"score":20,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-07-03T04:21:40.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: red;\"><blockquote>我希望南美足協能做點什麼</blockquote><br />\n</span><br />\n係咪想一個月搞一次"},{"pid":"87c927cea052ea72aad52d13d766f503818bdd85","tid":1280540,"uid":173952,"like":23,"dislike":0,"score":23,"quote":{"pid":"7db3e42e5cbc3767a9b958d3ddc889397f0a4677","tid":1280540,"uid":132264,"like":20,"dislike":0,"score":20,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-07-03T04:21:40.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: red;\"><blockquote>我希望南美